<L>__{interior roof, back of building day}
<A>__{on the sloping roof, szpilman clutches the skylight and has his feet in the roof gutter. he listens all quiet in the house. and then a bullet ricochets off the tiles beside him. szpilman, terrified, drops, involuntarily catching a lower edge so that his feet dangle above a balcony below. more shots. he drops on to the balcony and looks back.}
<L>__{exterior rooftop, two streets away day}
<A>__{two german soldiers are firing at szpilman.}
